motif var tl var spd var ac var af /obj to /basis \ add animation capability to everything

\ - Runtime rendering
: ?+ac delta spd @ p* ac +! ;
: keyframe { 0 me #children wrap me nth-child { draw } } ;
: animation ac @ p>s tl @ keyframe halt @ ?; ?+ac ;
: animate spd ! tl ! draw> animation ;

\ - Timeline definition
c: *timeline [locked] ;

\ - Keyframe definition w/ tile offset support
motif var tio /obj to /basis
: keyframe-ser ser> tio ? ." tio ! " ;
c: *keyframe keyframe-ser draw> tio @ tileofs ! ; 
